###########################
# 
# beCPG developers README
# 
###########################

0 - Setup project
------------------

Copy common.sh.sample to common.sh
and change properties


1 - Install development project
-------------------------------

To install becpg artifacts download https://becpg.fr/redmine/attachments/download/2/birt_3.7.1_lib.tar.gz
and extract jars into "becpg-bootstrap/lib".
 Then run install.sh

 
2 - Run project
----------------

./deploy-in-webapp.sh

cd $ALFRESCO
alfresco.sh start

3 - Test
---------
Run Junit tests :

mvn clean test -Dsurefire.useFile=false

Start report server :

cd becpg-report
mvn tomcat:run

Run specific test
cd becpg-core 
mvn clean test -Dsurefire.useFile=false -Dtest=MyTest.java